      <Statement>Explain what a point (&lt;i&gt;x&lt;/i&gt;, &lt;i&gt;y&lt;/i&gt;) on the graph of a proportional relationship means in terms of the situation, with special attention to the points (0, 0) and (1, &lt;i&gt;r&lt;/i&gt;) where r is the unit rate.</Statement>
